theorem closure_interior_idempotent_six {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior (closure (interior A)))))))))))) =
      closure (interior A) := by
  simp [Topology.closure_interior_idempotent]

theorem interior_closure_inter_comm {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A B : Set X) :
    interior (closure (A ∩ B : Set X)) =
      interior (closure (B ∩ A : Set X)) := by
  simpa [Set.inter_comm]
